      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 179.94,
      "start_time": 178.91,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 48,
      "text": "I don't wanna scare y'all."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 184.65,
      "start_time": 181.14,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 49,
      "text": "No, no, Michelle, the kids are, the kids are home from school."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 187.25,
      "start_time": 184.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 50,
      "text": "I, I have like six construction guys upstairs."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 188.93,
      "start_time": 187.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 51,
      "text": "I am way behind the work."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 189.97,
      "start_time": 188.94,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 52,
      "text": "So I'm sorry,"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 192.78,
      "start_time": 191.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 53,
      "text": "you could never scare us."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 194.36,
      "start_time": 193.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 54,
      "text": "Um,"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 200.44,
      "start_time": 195.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 55,
      "text": "thanks for setting up this call because we're um, I, yeah, I'm glad we could kind of talk through this."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 201.08,
      "start_time": 200.45,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 56,
      "text": "So,"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 205.2,
      "start_time": 202.93,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 57,
      "text": "hi, Alec, how are you, Michelle?"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 207.16,
      "start_time": 205.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 58,
      "text": "I'm good, good."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 207.63,
      "start_time": 207.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 59,
      "text": "You do it."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 211.22,
      "start_time": 208.16,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 60,
      "text": "It sounds like it's an interesting day over there and it's just,"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 214.23,
      "start_time": 212.37,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 61,
      "text": "it's all personal stuff, unfortunately."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 218.46,
      "start_time": 214.24,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 62,
      "text": "But yeah, it's, um, the work is, yeah, works a lot right now."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 228.94,
      "start_time": 218.64,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 63,
      "text": "Um So my, my leadership team, um, has sent out emails that I'm gonna be contacting people about A IQ this week, setting up trainings and all that."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 234.3,
      "start_time": 228.95,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 64,
      "text": "So that's why you'll probably see, you saw the one from Marsha and you're gonna see some more because, um, everyone's super excited."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 235.36,
      "start_time": 234.31,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 65,
      "text": "They want it yesterday."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 238.43,
      "start_time": 235.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 66,
      "text": "Um, um I'm working with Phil."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 240.55,
      "start_time": 238.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 67,
      "text": "I got an A VP call set up for Friday."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 242.34,
      "start_time": 240.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 68,
      "text": "I'm gonna set some more up for next week."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 252.32,
      "start_time": 242.63,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 69,
      "text": "Um So we're gonna be moving along pretty quickly and everyone I've talked to, even the people that my leaders thought might not be interested in using it are calling me asking to use it."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 257.1,
      "start_time": 252.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 70,
      "text": "So I'm pretty confident that we're gonna go nationwide pretty quickly."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 275.42,
      "start_time": 257.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 71,
      "text": "But the reason my, I, I sent that email yesterday because of course, you know, we're a new company now and they just wanna make sure we're not locked into something if there does become a time where maybe the Midwest says we would rather do something else because we're not making this um, a requirement."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 280.74,
      "start_time": 275.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 72,
      "text": "But it is going to be our, if you are not going to do it yourself, this is your only other option."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 284.76,
      "start_time": 280.75,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 73,
      "text": "So it is going to be the only, it is gonna be our preferred."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 288.33,
      "start_time": 284.78,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 74,
      "text": "Um We're calling it our preferred uh vendor."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 293.33,
      "start_time": 289.1,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 75,
      "text": "Um So if you wanna use a one, this one's been vetted, it's approved."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 295.21,
      "start_time": 293.34,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 76,
      "text": "Um A lot of people are excited about it."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 302.14,
      "start_time": 295.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 77,
      "text": "They are, they just wanna make sure we don't ramp up so quickly that all of a sudden we're paying for 100 and 80,000 units and only 100 end up going on."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 303.81,
      "start_time": 302.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 78,
      "text": "So they just wanna be careful about that."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 308.81,
      "start_time": 304.67,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 79,
      "text": "I'm confident that everyone's gonna go on, but I also don't own the company."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 315.34,
      "start_time": 308.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 80,
      "text": "So I have to, I have to give them, you know, they, they have done this a couple times before."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 322.47,
      "start_time": 315.35,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 81,
      "text": "So I just wanna make, that's what they wanted to ask about is can we pay um, per unit again?"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 327.42,
      "start_time": 322.48,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 82,
      "text": "I, I feel confident I'm gonna have at least half the company up in the next six weeks, if not sooner."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 330.17,
      "start_time": 327.52,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 83,
      "text": "And I believe it'll be more than that, but that'll be minimum."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 332.9,
      "start_time": 330.18,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 84,
      "text": "So this is not like, oh, we're not gonna put 10 sites on it."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 335.08,
      "start_time": 332.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 85,
      "text": "We're still gonna go up really, really quickly."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 339.46,
      "start_time": 336.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 86,
      "text": "Um They just asked for pricing if we were to do it that way."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 349.7,
      "start_time": 339.65,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 87,
      "text": "And they wanted to know if there was a difference in price, if you build us once a quarter a month or if you build the sites quarterly or monthly instead of us, they just wanted to kind of know all the details there."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 353.98,
      "start_time": 352.06,
      "recording_attendee_id": "f93b9e9b-b64c-4399-9d18-e66debb988e6",
      "order_number": 88,
      "text": "Got it in any additional context."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 354.37,
      "start_time": 353.99,
      "recording_attendee_id": "f93b9e9b-b64c-4399-9d18-e66debb988e6",
      "order_number": 89,
      "text": "Michelle."
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 373.11,
      "start_time": 354.38,
      "recording_attendee_id": "f93b9e9b-b64c-4399-9d18-e66debb988e6",
      "order_number": 90,
      "text": "Obviously, we're, I, I think we're both aligned like uh uh both parties trying to, to get to this national roll out any pushback, any new news other than just the re the request to uncover what, what uh what it could look like if you, if you don't go full, full roll out,"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
      "recording_id": "f6fd8ae9-07f3-4e23-a526-baf6f3e0beb4",
      "end_time": 375.88,
      "start_time": 374,
      "recording_attendee_id": "38263c8e-6719-4c37-9af1-861151a00864",
      "order_number": 91,
      "text": "can you, can we stop recording for a minute?"
    },
    {
      "id": "1daa54ae-7248-4f02-812c-23c6ff6cd3a0",
